initialize(address,uint256,string,string.notice: Initializes the store. Called immediately after cloning.

setSecondaryMintPrice(uint256).notice: Sets the price for secondary mints.

withdraw(address,uint256).notice: Withdraws ETH from the store to the creator or specified address.
